# Project Presentation

The analysis results of the dataset were visualized using **Looker Studio** and transformed into a presentation to communicate the key insights of the project.

The presentation summarizes the findings of the data analysis, highlights the factors affecting student performance, and provides visual explanations through charts and dashboards.

